name: log in
th: เข้าสู่ระบบ

name: enter your email to update password
zh-cn: 输入您的电子邮件以更新密码
en: Enter your email to update password

name: email sent to
zh-cn: 一封电子邮件已发送给您。 请检查您的收件箱并单击电子邮件中的链接进行验证。
en: An e-mail has been sent to you. Please check your inbox and click the link in the email to verify.

name: please check
zh-cn: 请检查您的收件箱并单击电子邮件中的链接进行验证。
en: Please check your inbox and click the link in the email to verify.

name: account exists
zh-cn: 存在具有此用户名的帐户

name: created not verified
zh-cn: 您的帐户已创建但尚未验证
en: Your account is created but not verified yet

name: username more than 2
zh-cn: 用户名必须超过 2 个字符
en: Username must be more than 2 characters

name: password has been updated
zh-cn: 密码已更新。 您可以立即登录！
en: Password has been updated. You may log in now!

name: invalid email or password
zh-cn: 无效的电子邮件或密码

name: account already verified
zh-cn: 帐户已验证。 请登录

name: confirmation link
zh-cn: 确认链接无效或已过期
en: The confirmation link is invalid or has expired

name: password must be 8 chars
zh-cn: 密码必须为 8 个字符或更多
en: Password must be 8 characters or more

name: email-activate
zh-cn: 欢迎光临！ 感谢您的注册。 请点击此链接激活您的帐户:
en: Welcome! Thanks for signing up. Please follow this link to activate your account:
